        "summary":  "Microsoft executive Jay Parikh argues that enterprise AI success depends on an integrated platform system, not individual AI models. The company unveiled a unified agent platform spanning GitHub, Microsoft IQ, Foundry, and Agent 365 to enable enterprises to build, contextualize, deploy, and continuously improve AI agents across business functions. The platform emphasizes governance, security, multi-model support, and continuous learning while giving enterprises operational control at scale.",
